817
00:50:45,300 --> 00:50:47,400
Da Yeon amat menyukaimu.

818
00:50:50,070 --> 00:50:51,940
Tidak perlu khawatir.

819
00:50:51,940 --> 00:50:54,039
Tanyakan saja langsung. Astaga.

820
00:50:54,409 --> 00:50:55,409
Baik.

